      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "While sacrificing your youth is heartbreaking, your life holds a dignity of love and history that no one else can provide even if you won't make a living wage. There is profound calm in accepting fate rather than fighting against it, but stepping away to let others live their lives adds a weight they are already carrying. It would be a tragedy if love were confused with survival loop; true selflessness is often the quiet joy of living your final chapters with someone willing to listen without judgment.",
